title: Walt Disney Treasures - Silly Symphonies (all of them)
description:
I believe that all of the Silly Symphonies and the More Silly Symphonies are here - in two different versions. The first version has the individual videos ripped from DVDs. The second version is in DVD format, one folder containing the Silly Symphonies and a second folder containing the More Silly Symphonies. However, this confuses me, since the Silly Symphonies and the More Silly Symphonies were each put out by Disney as a set of two DVDs. Therefore, this DVD version should include four folders, one for each DVD issued by Disney. Perhaps the people who created the torrents I downloaded merged the two DVDs in each set.

I have not done a thorough review of all the videos, so I don't know if any of the cartoons are missing or defective, or if the bonus features and the introductions by Leonard Maltin are included.

I look forward to comments by downloaders of this torrent about the above issue, about which version is preferred, and about the completeness and quality of the contents
